Dortmund sold South Korean Ji Dong Won to Augsburg on Monday while bringing in Slovenia midfielder Kevin Kampl from Red Bull Salzburg - who claims to have supported BVB since his childhood.

'It's great that it worked out,' the forward said on Sky. 

'I am delighted. I have been a BVB fanatic as a kid, and it's a dream fulfilled to be able to play for such an outstanding club.'

 

 

  

 

 

